title: Hyping Jets QB Mike White before TNF, Calling out the Chiefs, Can Saints make the playoffs, Nick Mangold and Fantasy picks
itunes:title: Hyping Jets QB Mike White before TNF, Calling out the Chiefs, Can Saints make the playoffs, Nick Mangold and Fantasy picks
description:
In the latest edition of the Good Morning Football Podcast, hosts Kay Adams, Kyle Brandt, Peter Schrager, and DeAngelo Hall are all about hyping up backup QB Mike White and the Jets, who open Week 9 against the Jets on Thursday Night. The crew doesn't want to count out the performances of head coaches this season while wondering if the Chiefs can rebound and if the Saints can make the playoffs. 7x Pro Bowl Center Nick Mangold helps preview the Jets and Kay answers fantasy football questions heading into Week 9.

The Good Morning Football Podcast is part of the NFL Podcast Network.
